title: PJ Warlock (Eclipse Comics fill)
description:
The ECUP jumps to the left, takes a step to the right, puts its hands on its hips, then brings its knees in tight, with 'PJ Warlock'!

Created by syndicated cartoonist Bill Schorr, PJ Warlock concerned itself with the misadventures of a bumbling wizard and his owl. Eclipse published three B&W issues from '86 to '87, all of which are included here.

Merci beaucoups to Mr. Schorr and the scanners! Git it and give it!
